:: Double-Decker-Dialogue [nobr]

<<if $sex.role == "Top">>
    <<ref _top 'subjCap'>> <<be _top>> underneath <<ref _bottom 'subj'>> as <<pro _bottom 'subj'>> stretch out on <<pro _bottom 'poss'>> back on the <<=_spot>>. <<pro _bottom 'obj' true >> lay their back on <<ref _top 'subjCap'>> like a recliner.

<<elseif $sex.role == "Bottom">>
    <<ref _bottom 'subjCap'>> are on <<ref _bottom 'poss'>> back on the <<=_spot>> atop <<ref _top 'subj'>>, laying on them like a recliner.
<</if>>